social_posts.post_text: If you knew how many times I lost it wouldn’t hurt you to see me win

My team & I just finished the floors and countertops on this new two story home upstairs and downstairs that’s currently for sale. A simple but luxurious job. Contact me for a remodel. We do travel as well.🛩✅

After & Before pics of a private pool area we finished this week. It took me and my team 4 1/2 days to complete it. It was a struggle at first but it turned out nice. Contact me for any remodeling needs.✅

My team and I just finished building this new restaurant from scratch in downtown Nashville.
The project took 2 long months but we got it done. Wild Wasabi is not open to the public just yet but it will be real soon. Contact me for a remodel we will have you covered.🤝
After & Before pics of this shower/wetroom I just finished. Starting the new year off booked on booked. Contact me for a remodel or a new install. ✅🤝
My first time tiling a firepit and using stones. Only took me 2 days and this family loves it. Contact me for a remodel or change if scenery to your home.🤝

Today I Lost My Granny One Of The Biggest Influences In My Life. My Gma Lived A Long Life And Went Out Happy. You Been Fighting Hard The Past 3 Weeks You Can Get Your Rest Now. Ima Keep Making You Proud Love You Granny 💔🤞🏾

Today makes 1 year since I became a flooring contractor and completed my 1st floor. A year ago around this time I was living a completely different life and wasn’t really sure where my life was headed so I decided to step out my comfort zone n try new things out. I always knew how to work with tools and etc just never saw myself being the one doing it. In one year I’ve changed my whole life around and have made alot of new connections and friendships along the way in the middle of this process I gained a team around that helped finished projects for me while i was out making connections. Never be afraid to start new things you’ll never know where it might take you in life. All it takes is 1 year. This is only the beginning. 🫡✅
